<paragraph id="3F9C52AE7A0AAC06DADA27D519A9C746" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Etymology.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="6C4179D21B949C3718A6C91047C5D34D" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Dedicated to Mr Hsi-Feng Lu, the member of TCRT who collected most specimens of this new species.</paragraph>
